tems. We also investigate the systematic error that arises from\nusing a model that neglects eccentricity when the signal is truly eccentric,\nfinding that the systematic error exceeds the statistical error in mass for\neccentricities as small as 0.02.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 18:46:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
