 and show that ${\\mathbf T}^{\\dagger}\nS_{\\gamma} {\\mathbf T}$ approximates $\\textrm{prox}_{\\|{\\mathbf T}\n\\cdot\\|_{1}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Oct 2019 07:25:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 08:00:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
